data.text:
Samsung Galaxy S6 Smartphones for Work or Play

All sorts of new smartphones are produced every year with impressive lists of features, but sometimes you just need used Samsung phones to take with you when you travel on vacation or business. eBay has all kinds of Samsung Galaxy S6 smartphones for sale. The Samsung S6 has multiple models and specifications.

Basic features of the affordable Samsung Galaxy S6

Here are some of the most important features of new, refurbished, and used Samsung Galaxy S6 smartphones. See the manufacturer's site for details.

Size: 5.65 inches by 2.78 inches by 0.27 inches.

Memory: 3 GB.

Storage Space: 32, 64, or 128 GB.

Display Size: 5.1 inches.

Battery: Li-ion 2,550 milliamp-hour battery.

Operating System: The phone originally came with Android 5.0.2, though it's also compatible with Android 6 and Android 7 operating systems.

Camera: 16 MP (f/1.9) 2160p rear camera.

Other versions of the Samsung Galaxy S6

Besides the standard Samsung Galaxy S6, there are other versions of the Galaxy Samsung put out: the Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge and Edge+. The Edge features a curved screen on one side for extra display, with the Edge+ being larger. Here are some specifics on the differences between them:

Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge: The Edge measures 5.59 inches by 2.76 inches by 0.38 inches. It comes with 3 GB of memory and either 32, 64, or 128 GB of storage space. It has a 5.1-inch screen and uses a Li-Ion 2,600 milliamp-hour battery. It was released running the Android 5.0.2 operating system, uses a 16 MP f/1.9 camera, and allows you to designate up to five contacts for quick access.

Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge+: The Edge+ measures 6.08 inches by 2.98 inches by 0.27 inches. It comes with 4 GB of memory and either 32 GB or 64 GB of storage space. It has a 5.7-inch screen and uses a Li-ion 3,000 milliamp-hour battery. It was released running the Android 5.1.1 operating system, uses a 16 MP f/1.9 camera, and allows you to designate up to five contacts for quick access.

Can you buy unlocked Samsung Galaxy S6 smartphones on eBay?

When a smartphone has been unlocked, it means that it is no longer tied to any specific service provider or use contract. If you have an unlocked smartphone, you'll have the freedom to shop around for new plans or carriers whenever you want. This includes foreign carriers, meaning that you can use an unlocked phone overseas. In general, an unlocked Samsung Galaxy S6 will have a slightly higher price than a locked Galaxy S6 in the same overall condition.
